vote.title: Authorize an Interlocal Agreement with Dallas County on behalf of Dallas County Health and Human Services in an amount not to exceed $2,273,350.00 to provide scattered site housing assistance for persons with HIV/AIDS for the period October 1, 2022 through September 30, 2023 - Not to exceed $2,273,350.00 - Financing: 2020-21 Housing Opportunities for Persons with AIDS Grant ($206,220.31), 2021-22 Housing Opportunities for Persons with AIDS Grant ($274,497.19), and 2022-23 Housing Opportunities for Persons with AIDS Grant ($1,792,632.50)
